### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@studentToken = 
@vendorToken = 

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AUTH ENDPOINTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Register Student
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/student
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "university": "MIT"
}

### Register Vendor
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/vendor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane's Cafe",
  "email": "vendor@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### Register Organizer
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/organizer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Event Manager",
  "email": "organizer@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "+0987654321",
  "institution": "Tech University"
}

### Login Student
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "student"
}

### Login Vendor
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vendor@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "vendor"
}

### Get Current User (Student)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

### Forgot Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### VENDOR ENDPOINTS (Requires Authentication)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create Vendor Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/vendor/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{vendorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "businessName": "Jane's Cafe",
  "description": "Premium coffee and pastries",
  "category": "Food & Beverage"
}

### Get My Vendor Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendor/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{vendorToken}}

### Update Vendor Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/vendor/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{vendorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "businessName": "Jane's Premium Cafe",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Update Contact Info
PUT {{baseUrl}}/vendor/profile/contact
Authorization: Bearer {{vendorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "email": "vendor@example.com"
}

### Update Delivery Settings
PUT {{baseUrl}}/vendor/profile/delivery
Authorization: Bearer {{vendorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryRadius": 5,
  "minOrder": 15
}

### Update Bank Details
PUT {{baseUrl}}/vendor/profile/bank
Authorization: Bearer {{vendorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountNumber": "1234567890",
  "routingNumber": "021000021",
  "accountName": "Jane Smith"
}

### Get Public Vendor Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/vendor/USER_ID/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

### Save Vendor (Student)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vendor/save
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vendorId": "VENDOR_ID_HERE"
}
